data.description: Welcome home to 15720 Hatfield Road. A raised ranch in the heart of Chippewa Township and Chippewa Local schools, on wide open private 2 ace lot with a elevated 12x32 rear deck. Large living room overlooks the spacious yard, updated kitchen with appliances, owners suite has its own full bath and includes a private sliding glass door to the deck area, their is also a finished lower level area with wood burning stove, some of the other improvements include furnace, AC, basement waterproofing with transferable warranty, and newer first floor flooring. A few rooms are left for you to complete your perfect finishing touches. Hurry today before someone swoops in and makes this their home.
